metadata.name: The battle of Houshang myth with the black demon
metadata.description:
The confrontation between the two armies is now in a tight situation. Demons know that the strength of the hero is beyond the rules of war and the hero knows that they fight unfairly.

Hand-drawn oil Painting on canvas.
